OpenBibArt

   The enhancement site "OpenBibArt" offers open access consultation, to
   all the bibliographical references from the Répertoire d'Art et
   d'Archéologie and from the Bibliographie d'Histoire de l'Art produced
   by INIST-CNRS.

   This site was designed for art historians, on an international scale,
   researchers and on a broader basis professionals and art lovers.

Coverage

   Bibliographie d'Histoire de l'Art
          Publication: 1991-2008

          Coverage: 1990-2007

          References: 401,523

   Répertoire d'Art et d'Archéologie
          Publication: 1973-1990

          Coverage: 1972-1989

          References: 208,000

   Répertoire d'art et d'archéologie numérisé (1910-1972)

Focus

   Bibliographic References:
          559750

   Documents :
          History General of art

          Middle Ages

          Renaissance, 17th and 18th centuries

          19th and 20th centuries

          Theory and sciences of art

          Aesthetics

          Psychology of art

          Sociology of art

          France

